fell within 2% of the predicted value from ab initio variational calculations reported
in the TheoReTS database (http://theorets.univ-reims.fr; http://theorets.tsu.ru).},
keywords = {High resolution spectra, CH, Methane, Octad, Long path FTIR,
Vibration-rotation states, Intensities, Infrared absorption, Effective Hamiltonian},
