	and M. Loete and L.R. Brown},
title = {{New assignments in the xxx transparency window of the 12CH4 Octad
	band system }},
journal = JQSRT,
year = {2013},
volume = {116},
pages = {101-109},
abstract = {This paper reports new assignments of rovibrational transitions of
	12CH4 bands in the range 4600Ã¢â‚¬â€œ4887 &#xa0;cm?1 which is usually
	referred to as a part of the 2&#xa0;?m methane transparency window.
	Several experimental data sources for methane line positions and
